  Game information:
  =================

  In latter-day Hong Kong, a policeman goes missing. The department is
  dumbfounded by the disappearance until they receive what appears to be a
  ransom call from an unnamed source. The kidnapper requests that a single
  officer appear in Kowloon market. Tequila volunteers for the assignment,
  beginning a sequence of battles with rival Triads and the Russian Mafia that
  extends from the street markets of Hong Kong to the museums of Chicago.
